## Parity Tests

Parity tests between backtester exit rules and the exit engine are critical for RL training. Agents must see identical behavior in training vs live execution.

```python
@pytest.mark.parametrize("scenario", PARITY_TEST_CASES)
def test_backtester_matches_exit_engine(scenario):
    bt_result = backtester.run(scenario)
    engine_result = exit_engine.evaluate(scenario)
    assert bt_result.exits == engine_result.exits
```

