## Package Dependencies

### gymnasium (not gym)

The `gymnasium` package is the maintained fork of OpenAI Gym. Always import from `gymnasium`.

```python
# WRONG: Legacy package
import gym

# RIGHT: Maintained fork
import gymnasium as gym
```

### MaskablePPO Requires sb3-contrib

`MaskablePPO` is in `sb3-contrib`, not `stable-baselines3`.

```python
from sb3_contrib import MaskablePPO
from sb3_contrib.common.maskable.policies import MaskableActorCriticPolicy
```

