## SB3 Compatibility Testing

Test SB3 compatibility early in development.

```python
def test_sb3_compatibility():
    env = YourTradingEnv(config)
    try:
        model = MaskablePPO("MlpPolicy", env)
        model.learn(total_timesteps=100)
    except Exception as e:
        pytest.fail(f"SB3 incompatible: {e}")
```

