## Frozen Dataclass Collection Fields

When using `@dataclass(frozen=True)`, collection fields cannot use `set` (unhashable). Use `tuple` instead:

```python
# WRONG: sets are unhashable, breaks frozen=True
@dataclass(frozen=True)
class Decision:
    tags: set[str]

# CORRECT: tuples are hashable
@dataclass(frozen=True)
class Decision:
    tags: tuple[str, ...]
```
